data.title: Full-Time Sports Dietitians - ASPDA
data.meta_description: Below is a list of sports dietitians working directly with athletes for 40 or more hours per week in the major college conferences, with professional sports teams, with Olympic athletes and within the U.S. military. ASPDA has tracked the growth of Sports RDs over time. Click Here to view a visual representation of this growth. […]
data.meta_site_name: ASPDA | SportsRd.org | American Sports and Performance Dietitians Association
